===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|abissus|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{term|abyssus||a bottomless gulf|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἄβυσσος||bottomless|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ἀ-||not|lang=grc}}+ {{term|βυσσός||deep place|lang=grc}},<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=11}}</ref>,<ref name=AHD>{{R:American Heritage 1971|page=6}}</ref> from {{term|βυθός||deep place|lang=grc}}.<ref name=WI3>{{R:MW3 1976|page=9}}</ref>

